column5: A buddy of mine from Winnipeg sent this to me Caught a few days ago  33" long 25" girth  http://www.youtube.com/catsontheredcanada   rick
for sure that is one real beauty
holy COW  It's amazing something that big can come out of a hole that small.
It was released, they were covering its eyes trying to get it into a shack to take photos, so they eye didn't freeze in the cold.
Thanks Rick....lol...to make it worse it was actually with Stu Mckay of Catsonthered that we were meant to be meeting up with....DOH!!!
Ohhhhhhh that's gotta hurt.    Hopefully you'll get another opportunity simon.  That's a tank of an walleye.
Wow!  Gotta be the biggest eye I've ever seen through the ice.  Thanks for the video.
WOW...a true monster through the ice....That might have been tricky to get out if he were by himself.  Cheers  Craig
that is one hell of fish, simply outstandingb
